{"sections":{"main":{"type":"hero-alt","blocks":{"7afbc083-9569-43ab-892c-b53616f7bbb7":{"type":"text","settings":{"subtitle":"WHERE NOSTALGIA MEETS UNDERSTATED GLAMOUR","title":"Galaxy","content":"<p>FAE envisions the charming 80's jet-set influenced by the glitzy high life and late summer sun.<\/p>","button_style":"button--filled","button_text":"View more","button_url":"\/","button_separator":true}},"3a3cdb7a-6cdf-4afb-8964-e4e108aed256":{"type":"media","settings":{}}},"block_order":["7afbc083-9569-43ab-892c-b53616f7bbb7","3a3cdb7a-6cdf-4afb-8964-e4e108aed256"],"settings":{"hero_alt_banner_height":50,"section_width":"page","color_scheme":"scheme-4","spacing_top":"2","spacing_bottom":"2","section_border":"none"}},"rich_text_fzytDz":{"type":"rich-text","name":"t:sections.rich-text.name","settings":{"layout":"normal","heading":"Explore the season","heading_size":"h2","content":"<p>Starring Natasja Madsen and her zest for life in a luxurious world of charming energy and late night summer glam. Set against the backdrop of Antigua's dreamy caribbean coastline.<\/p><p>Daringly designed to charm the sensual side of all who wear them, this collection welcomes new silhouettes cut to perfection, alongside the core FAE styles you all know and love. From minimal string bikinis to streamline detailed paneling, slip into a steamy new season of FAE, and enter the a collection out of this world… the Galaxy yacht awaits.<\/p><p>Shot by Sam Dameshek, it is officially time to celebrate the hedonism of another hot n’ steamy season of FAE. <\/p>","content_position":"center","section_width":"narrow","color_scheme":"scheme-1","spacing_top":"1","spacing_bottom":"1","section_border":"none"}},"9ab88629-dd5e-4904-a9ce-81bb423d858c":{"type":"full-width-banner","blocks":{"template--18166283698491__9ab88629-dd5e-4904-a9ce-81bb423d858c-1677686851cd9bf7cc-0":{"type":"subtitle","settings":{}},"template--18166283698491__9ab88629-dd5e-4904-a9ce-81bb423d858c-1677686851cd9bf7cc-1":{"type":"title","set